Package: CampbellLogger
Title: Imports, combines Campbell logger files
Version: 0.0.3.0.1
Author: Markus Loew [aut, cre]
Authors@R: c(person("Markus", "Loew", email = "m.loew@unimelb.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Import individual Campbell Scientific *.dat files from a CR1000
    data logger (specific to the AgFace experiment), or import and merge multiple
    files of the same log-interval. Calculates sunrise and sunset at AgFace location
    for any given date. This package is specific to the CR1000 logger configuration
    of the AgFace experiment.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Imports:
    plyr,
    reshape2,
    ggplot2,
    readr,
    sp,
    suntools
Suggests:
    parallel
Maintainer: Markus Loew <m.loew@unimelb.edu.au>
URL: https://github.com/MarkusLoew/CampbellLogger
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
